# Project Name

## Overview

This project is a Spring Boot application that connects to a MySQL database. To run this project, you'll need to have Eclipse with the Spring Tool Suite 4 plugin installed, as well as MySQL Workbench.

## Prerequisites

1. **Eclipse with Spring Tool Suite 4**
   - Download and install [Eclipse IDE](https://www.eclipse.org/downloads/packages/).
   - Install the [Spring Tool Suite 4 plugin](https://spring.io/tools).

2. **MySQL Workbench**
   - Download and install [MySQL Workbench](https://dev.mysql.com/downloads/workbench/).

